#Automation practice - Add to cart

## Search for t-shirt and add to cart from product page
* Open application
* Click "Women" menu item
* Verify "WOMEN" search category is displayed
* Open product with title "Faded Short Sleeve T-shirts"
* Verify "Faded Short Sleeve T-shirts" product page is displayed
* Specify product quantity as "2"
* Specify product size as "M"
* Click add to cart button in product page
* Verify Added to cart message
* Click Proceed to Checkout button in 'Added to cart' modal window
* Verify Shopping Cart Sumamry page is displayed
* Verify product details Name = "Faded Short Sleeve T-shirts", Size = "M", Quantity = "2"